_sText:
This is a CS:S remake of one of my favorite CS 1.6 FY maps.  The scale and textures are a little different, but the layout is identical to the original.

This is a very fast paced map with many weapons on the upper level (spawn), Grenades and a Buyzone are in the middle on the lower level.  

Please note this map was designed for super-fast "kill it if it moves" games.  Expect rounds to last no longer than 30 seconds

Original author credited in the map.
